    "attributes": {
        "action": "Compulsory standard charger style for all rechargeable electronic devices.",
        "additional_details": "The Government should ban the manufacture and sale of rechargeable electronic devices that do not accommodate the standard charger. \r\n\r\nWe are dumping millions of items per year into landfill. This must stop.",
        "background": "Why can't we have a standard industry charger that fits all rechargeable electronic items. The EU had a commitment from manufacturers to support this however this has stalled. ",
